div.p: Group 1 Mapping from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/Parameters|5.0.0 to unspecified code system

tr.td: FHIR R5 Resource `Parameters` is representable via FHIR R4B Resource `Parameters`. Element `Parameters` is mapped to FHIR R4B element `Parameters`.
